<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.198617>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Mesodorylaimus khasianus n. sp. A: Entire female. B: Entire male. C: Anterior region. D: Anterior end showing amphid. E: Expanded part of pharynx. F: Coelomocytes. G: Female genital branch (posterior). H: Vulval region. I: Female posterior region. J: Male posterior region. K: Male tail." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/198617/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.198618>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Mesodorylaimus khasianus n. sp. A: Anterior region. B: Pharyngo-intestinal junction. C-D: Vulval region. E: Female prerectum. F: Female posterior region. G: Male posterior region. H: Male tail." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/198618/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

